    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense, but I've heard some folks in the industry say that focusing on \"existential risk\" is a massive distraction from more immediate issues, or even that the whole concept is just speculative hype used to justify heavy-handed government control. How would you respond to that?",
